Yeah, it's a festival, but I'd best be
careful. If Kris sees me pullin' too
many pranks, I'm in for an earful.

Humans pass away in the blink of an
eye. It's always sad to say goodbye.
For now... I'll try to enjoy this festival.

Looks like Tiki's havin' fun. Seems
like her nightmares've died down
too. I'm glad she made some friends.

Trick or treat! Better make with the
candy quick. My tricks'll make your
head spin!

Who should I change into next... A
kid'd have the best chance of makin'
off with tons of candy, but...hmm...$k$pEr... Were you listening?

Name's Xane. I'm havin' lots of
fun at the harvest festival over at
$Nf's castle!
Nothin' better than a good trick!

Think you're clever, do ya?
You'll never see through my
tricks!
Now that's no good.

I'm not helpin' humans that easily.
But you're someone I can trust.

I'm Xane. I can change into
anybody—even you! Wanna see?
It'll make the festival a lot more fun!

You're not angry that I disguised
myself as a whole bunch'a Heroes
and filled up on candy, are you?$k$pYou can't hold that against me!
Tricks like those are what the
festival is all about.$k$pSee, humans don't have long to
live, so they have to figure out
how they WANT to live.$k$pYou can't spend all your time fightin'.
You need to fool around every once
in a while too!$k$pLook at me! I have hundreds of years
set aside just for pulling pranks and
goofin' off.

The name's Xane. The princey and me go way back. Oh, I mean Marth.
Whoa! Tryin' to scare me? You've got some guts.
This world sure has a lot of festivals... I'm not sayin' it's a bad thing.
You're lookin' at a bona-fide master of mischief. Who should I impersonate next?
Where am I from? Well... Let's just say, not from around here. Not even close.
This world's BURSTIN' with stuff, isn't it? I'll never get bored!
I look good like this? Aw, cut it out, you. You're makin' me blush!
